"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月10日消息，权益池和DEX跨链协议Umbria Network宣布推出一个名为Connect Portal的新工具，允许用户自动将MetaMask钱包连接到任何EVM兼容链，比如 Polygon、Binance Smart Chain、Avalanche等。Connect Portal还会提供有关连接EVM链的其他信息，例如chainID、以及与网络本地[区块链](https://www.bitcoin86.com/block/)浏览器的链接。\",\"timestamp\":1639118436,\"title\":\"Umbria Network推出EVM兼容链MetaMask自动配置工具\"},\"digest\":\"ijxRf3XfMNTmvXSxj7Urnh6iruHk8sgYG2F2QXasX8U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2F03a8266a7d4F69400306C6e99c466172110B77\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fNGQH4OwWA6NlEAHJdgJVQOW617EAk9TBQaJJYSAPJo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sdZ3PJ2Cdj7wrMiwsgkxvUgoUsE-RbhtuvkXLJEAyB0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"cufr_2jdu4ljwbwpj2uVq6KDWAk6mRTW0MaChLOTeqiZDGNWuGSSv2SWsqkbBrQ1Y798s_9xGhpUgrJ3tTdHbw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa107b836dc61eb933beb77ba27a6ca46874b721e70be67841812fcd5af02c2196bfd685ad6ec7308147c7b32ca81af327d6e8b886972a1f4cbd7c6a890d75aac1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fNGQH4OwWA6NlEAHJdgJVQOW617EAk9TBQaJJYSAPJo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sdZ3PJ2Cdj7wrMiwsgkxvUgoUsE-RbhtuvkXLJEAyB0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ijxRf3XfMNTmvXSxj7Urnh6iruHk8sgYG2F2QXasX8U\"}"